===Etymology===
From [[spore]] + [[-phyte]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{botany}} The [[plant]] (or the [[diploid]] [[phase]] in its [[life cycle]]) which produces [[spore]]s by [[meiosis]] in order to produce [[gametophyte]]s.

